channel.title: Need help setting up rsps on vps!
channel.description:
so i bought a vps 2 days ago,a centOS 6 64-bit linux. i followed a tutorial and installed the jdk on it,now i uploaded my source but i get this error when i run it,
Exception in thread "main" java.lang.NoClassDefFoundError: com/alex/store/Store at com.rs.cache.Cache.init(Cache.java:19) at com.rs.Launcher.main(Launcher.java:64) Caused by: java.lang.ClassNotFoundException: com.alex.store.Store at java.net.URLClassLoader$1.run(URLClassLoader.java:202) at java.security.AccessController.doPrivileged(Native Method) at java.net.URLClassLoader.findClass(URLClassLoader.java:190) at java.lang.ClassLoader.loadClass(ClassLoader.java:306) at sun.misc.Launcher$AppClassLoader.loadClass(Launcher.java:301) at java.lang.ClassLoader.loadClass(ClassLoader.java:247) ... 2 more
whats the problem? :/
